1
00:01:27,470 --> 00:01:31,940
[The Dark Romance]

2
00:01:32,190 --> 00:01:34,890
[Episode 12]

3
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:54,120
[The Cutest One in the World]

4
00:01:50,229 --> 00:01:51,680
I know you're angry.

5
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:54,440
But can you give me a chance to explain?

6
00:01:56,590 --> 00:01:57,430
I'm sorry.

7
00:01:58,509 --> 00:01:59,310
In the future,

8
00:01:59,740 --> 00:02:02,930
[The Cutest One in the World]

9
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:01,350
will I still have the chance to treat you

10
00:02:01,350 --> 00:02:03,010
to the loving lunch made by me?

11
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,960
What terrible cooking?

12
00:02:23,630 --> 00:02:24,750
The egg is even burnt.

13
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:29,370
[Lihai Meteorology]

14
00:02:39,470 --> 00:02:41,270
-Be careful on the way.
-Bye bye.

15
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:45,810
What are you doing here?

16
00:02:45,810 --> 00:02:47,150
I brought you some fruit salad.

17
00:02:47,150 --> 00:02:48,010
I don't want it.

18
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,430
There are many raisins in it.

19
00:02:49,430 --> 00:02:50,290
I don't want it.

20
00:02:52,820 --> 00:02:55,140
Have you seen that news recently?

21
00:02:56,150 --> 00:02:58,440
The PUA Class? Undercover agents, right?

22
00:02:58,440 --> 00:02:59,470
I saw the news.

23
00:02:59,930 --> 00:03:01,710
The informant inside there was you, right?

24
00:03:01,710 --> 00:03:02,290
Yes.

25
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:05,840
So the person Chen Xue saw that day
was you.

26
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:06,840
You were afraid of being exposed,

27
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,960
so you colluded with Yan Ling
to lie to me.

28
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,240
Yes, I was lying to you.

29
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,240
You even said yes?

30
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:12,680
No, no, no.

31
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,140
But I...

32
00:03:13,590 --> 00:03:15,280
But I really didn't mean that
when I said it.

33
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,280
What did you mean?

34
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:19,860
I'd like to see how you'll explain it.

35
00:03:21,150 --> 00:03:21,680
Well...

36
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,680
Don't be angry.

37
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,200
Look.

38
00:03:28,870 --> 00:03:31,100
That news was so unclear,

39
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,980
but you could still recognize me.

40
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:36,000
It means you still care about me.

41
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,650
How can you be like this?

42
00:03:38,640 --> 00:03:39,079
So...

43
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:40,740
You think it's over like this?

44
00:03:41,310 --> 00:03:42,710
That was clearly a heroic act.

45
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:44,570
Why couldn't you just tell me?

46
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:45,710
Well...

47
00:03:45,710 --> 00:03:46,400
I know.

48
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,520
You were afraid
I'd mess things up for you.

49
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,020
No!

50
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,840
Or were you afraid I'd stop you?

51
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,280
That thing was too dangerous.

52
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,079
If I had told you,

53
00:03:53,079 --> 00:03:54,520
wouldn't you worry about me?

54
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,520
Also, um...

55
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:59,180
In order to infiltrate the enemy,

56
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:01,840
I had to do some bad things,

57
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,570
which were even a little dirty.

58
00:04:04,310 --> 00:04:04,860
Look.

59
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:06,490
You are so innocent

60
00:04:06,910 --> 00:04:08,000
and quite naive.

61
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,680
I was afraid...

62
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:13,710
So you and Yan Ling are adults,

63
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:16,680
