64
00:04:17,630 --> 00:04:18,070
No.

65
00:04:18,070 --> 00:04:19,070
I'm almost 30.

66
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,480
And you're still saying that I'm naive.

67
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:22,190
You might as well just call me stupid.

68
00:04:22,190 --> 00:04:22,820
No, no, no.

69
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,070
I didn't mean that.

70
00:04:24,070 --> 00:04:24,800
Let go.

71
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:26,870
Let go!

72
00:04:34,070 --> 00:04:36,130
What will we have for dinner tonight?

73
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:38,120
We haven't even had breakfast yet,

74
00:04:38,150 --> 00:04:39,920
