75
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,980
It's too hot today.

76
00:04:41,510 --> 00:04:43,110
Let's eat cold rice noodles.

77
00:04:46,630 --> 00:04:48,630
Why do you suddenly want to eat this?

78
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:50,830
Dr. Luo asked us

79
00:04:50,830 --> 00:04:52,830
