80
00:04:53,830 --> 00:04:55,090
Dr. Luo came to see you?

81
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:57,560
No.

82
00:04:58,270 --> 00:05:00,400
He hasn't come to see me for a long time.

83
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:04,430
I just want to ask about this.

84
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,850
Will I still have a chance to eat

85
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:10,550
the Sweet and Sour Ribs
made by Uncle Luo Liang?

86
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,160
His cooking tastes just the same

87
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,090
as Godmother's.

88
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:27,630
[The problem has been solved.
I'll wash the outfit and return it to you.]

89
00:05:27,660 --> 00:05:28,300
[Okay. No hurry.]

90
00:05:28,330 --> 00:05:29,030
[Thank you for today.]

91
00:05:29,140 --> 00:05:33,040
[Dr. Luo Liang]

92
00:05:39,090 --> 00:05:41,560
[Dr. Luo Liang]

93
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:41,690
[3 days ago]

94
00:05:41,690 --> 00:05:42,520
[Thank you for trusting me
and telling me your story.]

95
00:05:42,550 --> 00:05:43,990
[Rest early.]

96
00:05:48,950 --> 00:05:50,390
Can we talk again?

97
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:53,159
It's really not like what you think.

98
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,220
It's because...

99
00:05:58,820 --> 00:06:04,180
[Typing...]

100
00:06:08,610 --> 00:06:09,780
[Can we talk again?]

101
00:06:09,810 --> 00:06:11,210
[It's really not like what you think.
It's because...]

102
