[Typing...]

103
00:06:42,610 --> 00:06:45,100
[Dongchuan Public Security Department]

104
00:06:45,170 --> 00:06:47,390
[Interrogation Room 1]

105
00:06:50,490 --> 00:06:52,730
[Interrogation Room 1]

106
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:02,970
You can do it.

107
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:23,570
[Interrogator] [Scribe]

108
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,680
I'm warning you guys!

109
00:07:29,390 --> 00:07:30,590
I'm a Pazion citizen.

110
00:07:30,870 --> 00:07:33,800
I demand that you should notify
the Pazion Consulate immediately.

111
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,800
If the people from the consulate
don't come,

112
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,190
I won't say a word.

113
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:42,430
According to Article 6 of the Criminal Law

114
00:07:42,430 --> 00:07:44,240
of the People's Republic of China,

115
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,190
foreigners who commit crimes

116
00:07:45,190 --> 00:07:47,600
within Chinese territory
are subject to this law,

117
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:50,090
except as otherwise

118
00:07:50,630 --> 00:07:52,360
specifically provided by law.

119
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:56,720
Do you think you're special enough?

120
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,700
What do you want me to call you?

121
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,480
Xia Yi,

122
00:08:12,630 --> 00:08:13,800
Pongsri Leekpa,

123
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:15,160
or...

124
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:16,630
Lin Huosheng?

125
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:21,800
Lin Huosheng is the name
on the Chinese household register.

126
00:08:22,070 --> 00:08:23,120
Pongsri Leekpa

127
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:25,610
is the name in Pazion
after the plastic surgery.

128
00:08:25,610 --> 00:08:26,780
Xia Yi

129
00:08:27,020 --> 00:08:29,420
is the alias for fraud
in the outside world.

130
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:30,390
Right?

131
00:08:30,850 --> 00:08:32,980
[Interrogator]

132
00:08:35,669 --> 00:08:36,669
Bank statements.

133
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:44,120
We've obtained
Jian Leilei's bank statements

134
00:08:43,490 --> 00:08:44,680
[Lihai Commercial Bank
Account Historical Transaction Statement]

135
00:08:44,750 --> 00:08:46,000
The records show that

136
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:47,960
the first 500,000 yuan

137
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:50,490
she had transferred
out of a client's account

138
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:52,950
was withdrawn in cash at the counter.

139
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,430
A day later,

140
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,420
[Lihai Commercial Bank
Account Historical Transaction Statement]

141
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:57,390
your bank account
in the name of Lin Huosheng

142
00:08:57,390 --> 00:09:00,030
just received a 500,000 cash deposit.

143
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,390
You've really mastered

144
00:09:06,390 --> 00:09:09,030
this trick and used it so well.

145
00:09:09,770 --> 00:09:11,230
While dating Jian Leilei,

146
00:09:11,910 --> 00:09:13,910
you gave her fake luxury goods
as gifts first

147
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:15,840
and then asked her to lend you cash.

148
00:09:16,870 --> 00:09:18,630
Usually, girls in this situation

149
00:09:18,630 --> 00:09:20,480
find it hard to refuse you, right?

150
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,320
After that,

151
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:24,030
via small transfers,

152
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:26,030
you returned a little money to her
in installments

153
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:26,830
to build trust

154
00:09:27,270 --> 00:09:28,960
and pave the way for a bigger loan later.

155
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:31,600
Meanwhile,
it could also leave transfer records,

156
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,080
making it look like

157
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:35,220
she was borrowing money from you.

158
00:09:38,030 --> 00:09:38,720
Am I right?

159
00:09:40,630 --> 00:09:41,960
She did it voluntarily.

160
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,370
I couldn't help it, either.

161
00:09:44,910 --> 00:09:48,970
That's because she fell in love with me
after sleeping with me a few times.

162
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,160
Do you like it?

163
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,090
Yes, I do.

164
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,600
Will you marry me?

165
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,890
Yes, I will.

166
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:16,810
Thank you for saying yes to me.

167
00:10:23,210 --> 00:10:24,750
I didn't expect that

168
00:10:26,510 --> 00:10:28,110
you would distrust me so much

169
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:30,340
when we were about to get married.

170
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:36,550
Honey, of course I trust you.

171
00:10:36,550 --> 00:10:38,390
Otherwise,
I wouldn't have mortgaged the house

172
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:39,690
to support you.

173
00:10:39,910 --> 00:10:42,910
But your investment
really keeps losing money.

174
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:44,950
If you need projects,

175
00:10:45,150 --> 00:10:47,210
I still have a few clients at the bank.

176
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,980
Don't mention your clients to me.

177
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,240
As you got those clients

178
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,630
by flirting and smiling,

179
00:10:53,630 --> 00:10:54,910
can they even be considered as clients?

180
00:10:54,910 --> 00:10:56,200
How could you think of me like that?

181
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:58,030
You forced me to think like that.

182
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:01,840
Let me tell you,

183
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:02,570
Jian Leilei.

184
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:05,030
Don't think that working at the bank

185
00:11:05,030 --> 00:11:06,270
gives you the right to

186
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:07,730
meddle in my investments.

187
00:11:07,790 --> 00:11:08,910
I've handled more money

188
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:10,840
than you could see in your lifetime!

189
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:11,910
Honey, you've misunderstood.

190
00:11:11,910 --> 00:11:13,750
I really didn't mean that.

191
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:15,600
I really don't think that way.

192
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,560
Then what do you mean?

193
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,410
You just look down on me, don't you?

194
00:11:19,410 --> 00:11:20,750
No, I don't.

195
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,460
Why am I working so hard?

196
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:23,240
Because I just want to

197
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:24,480
prove to my parents

198
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:25,120
that without them,

199
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,380
I can still make money,

200
00:11:27,270 --> 00:11:27,670
and without them,

201
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:29,720
I can also marry the woman I love.

202
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,270
Only in this way

203
00:11:31,270 --> 00:11:32,430
can I avoid seeing

204
00:11:32,430 --> 00:11:33,270
those rich girls they've picked out,

205
00:11:33,270 --> 00:11:35,500
whose families match mine in status.

206
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:36,930
Do you know that?

207
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:37,860
Yes, I know.

208
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,820
But I didn't expect that

209
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,970
just like them,
you would also disbelieve me.

210
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:49,790
Honey, I really didn't mean that.

211
00:11:49,790 --> 00:11:50,870
I'm sorry.

212
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:53,000
What's wrong? Let me take a look.

213
00:11:54,510 --> 00:11:56,370
How did you get injured like this?

214
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,450
Does it hurt?

215
00:12:01,510 --> 00:12:02,440
In your opinion,

216
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:05,570
if I hadn't been so desperate,

217
00:12:06,870 --> 00:12:08,530
would I borrow money from you?

218
00:12:11,310 --> 00:12:12,970
Did you borrow money outside?

219
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:19,240
They say marriage is a gamble.

220
00:12:21,390 --> 00:12:22,720
I've bet everything I have

221
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:25,070
and might even need to bet my life soon.

222
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:26,120
But what about you,

223
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:26,850
Jian Leilei?

224
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,840
What have you done for our family?

225
00:12:32,870 --> 00:12:33,600
Don't worry.

226
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:36,930
I will never drag you into this.

227
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:39,670
Honey!

228
00:12:39,670 --> 00:12:41,630
Don't leave. Honey!

229
00:12:41,630 --> 00:12:43,290
Don't leave! I'm begging you!

230
00:12:43,390 --> 00:12:45,120
I'll definitely find a solution.

231
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:48,240
Don't leave.
I'll definitely find a solution.

232
00:12:52,630 --> 00:12:54,560
You have no idea how much I love you.

233
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,240
Besides,

234
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:27,260
I also didn't force her
to embezzle her clients' money.

235
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:29,120
I really didn't know about this.

236
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,240
She's a mid‑level employee at the bank,

237
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,570
and at this age,

238
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:35,840
logically speaking,
she should be quite rich.

239
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:38,330
Unexpectedly, she had so little savings.

240
00:13:39,270 --> 00:13:41,120
So in order to cheat more money

241
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:42,600
out of Jian Leilei,

242
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:45,150
you sent her

243
00:13:45,150 --> 00:13:47,350
the intimate videos you had taken of her

244
00:13:47,550 --> 00:13:49,910
and kept blackmailing and threatening her,

245
00:13:49,910 --> 00:13:52,030
saying that you'd expose the videos
if she didn't pay,

246
00:13:52,030 --> 00:13:54,290
until you finally drove her to her death.

247
00:13:57,670 --> 00:13:59,800
After Jian Leilei committed suicide,

248
00:13:59,910 --> 00:14:01,960
I was planning to just leave.

249
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:04,550
But I listened to Yu Kexin,
that wretched woman,

250
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:06,010
and played along with her.

251
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:08,720
Otherwise,
you wouldn't have been able to find me.

252
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:10,600
Don't retreat.
They're already targetting you.

253
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:11,150
Just fight back first.

254
00:14:11,150 --> 00:14:12,410
I'm not fighting back.

255
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:13,800
I need to run away now.

256
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:14,440
If you run away,

257
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:16,170
I'll just get trapped, won't I?

258
00:14:17,740 --> 00:14:18,920
What did I say?

259
00:14:19,150 --> 00:14:20,880
If we don't run away, we'll die.

260
00:14:23,650 --> 00:14:25,580
We're doomed this time, aren't we?

261
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:26,820
What a coward.

262
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,360
You're exactly the same as before.

263
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:30,000
When things go wrong,
you tend to just run away.

264
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,390
You haven't improved at all.

265
00:14:31,390 --> 00:14:32,390
That woman surnamed Yan

266
00:14:32,390 --> 00:14:33,870
tracked me down through the tattoo.

267
00:14:33,870 --> 00:14:34,790
If you don't fight back,

268
00:14:34,790 --> 00:14:36,120
we're both going to die.

269
00:14:45,230 --> 00:14:45,350
[Lihai Commercial Bank
Account Historical Transaction Statement]

270
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:45,800
[Wanderer's Exclusive Love Course]

271
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,270
Are you very proud of

272
00:14:47,270 --> 00:14:48,120
this contemptible

273
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:49,960
PUA Theory you've invented?

274
00:14:50,270 --> 00:14:51,670
The entire telecom fraud group

275
00:14:51,670 --> 00:14:53,790
was established
on the basis of your theory.

276
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:54,650
Let me tell you!

277
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:57,320
The amount of money
involved in this case is huge.

278
00:14:57,320 --> 00:14:58,440
